metadata.name: SHAPES&PATTERNS V1 – PT.1
metadata.description:
SHAPES&PATTERNS V1 – PT.1

A self initiated project of nine 1/1s, originally only going to be R&D for my iconic cloth style, using the original supplied textures through a CC by 4.0 license from https://normform.art/.

Following tons of feedback, I recreated them with my own couple twists, while keeping their original colour schemes and stylistic approach alive.

This series is my first real art collection. 

Thanks to all my friends and fans of my work for your unreal support, this goes out to you.
